nhwHack Beer'd
nhr-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ncAvast, ye LAN lubbers! Grab a grog and park yer ParrotOS while cap'n
ncHackBeer'd tells a `tail -f /dev/urandom`.
nwThe most infamous hacker buccaneer on the seven networks. Sailed with a crew
nwincluding Bobby TABLES. Accompanied by a parrot named Pollymorphic.

nhwDustin Heywood (EvilMog)
nhr-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ncThe Early Hashcat Beta Days, the Rise of the Alberta Hashcat Super Cluster,
ncDROWN, and More
nwSenior Technical Leader at IBM X-Force. Semi-retired Team Hashcat member.
nwBishop of the Church of Wifi. Multi-time Hacker Jeopardy World Champion.
nwBlack Badge collector.

